<b><big><u>Property Description</u></big></b><br><br>
Find a remarkable setting perfect for your enjoyment at Wellington Farm Apartments. Situated charmingly in Charlotte, NC with so much to do all over, We are close to downtown and UNCC. Living at this community provides you a diverse variety of nearby experiences to check out. Select from 1 and 2 bedroom apartment options. Call us for current rates or schedule a tour to see your favorite. Our community also displays plenty of top apartment community features like the clubhouse, laundry facility, and relaxing swimming pool, fitness center and more. Start your move now!<br><br>
